    • Bloco

      public Bloco(String curso, String uc, String turno, String turma, int inscritos, String diaSemana, LocalTime horaIni, LocalTime horaFim, LocalDate data, String sala, int lotacao)
      Creates a new instance of the Bloco class with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      curso - a string representing the course(s) associated with the block.
      uc - a string representing the course unit (subject) associated with the block.
      turno - a string representing the shift associated with the block.
      turma - a string representing the class group associated with the block.
      inscritos - an integer representing the number of enrolled students in the block.
      diaSemana - a string representing the day of the week for the block.
      horaIni - a LocalTime object representing the start time of the block.
      horaFim - a LocalTime object representing the end time of the block.
      data - a LocalDate object representing the date associated with the block.
      sala - a string representing the room associated with the block.
      lotacao - an integer representing the capacity/limit of the room.
